I heard you!

312
00:21:59,480 --> 00:22:01,200
Come on, you stupid voice.

313
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:03,880
"Harold frantically grabbed his lamp.

314
00:22:04,850 --> 00:22:09,310
Harold, incensed, shook the hell
