331
00:23:22,900 --> 00:23:26,030
No, not to me, about me.

332
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:31,440
I'm somehow involved
in some sort of story.

333
00:23:31,840 --> 00:23:34,400
Like I'm a character in my own life.

334
00:23:34,940 --> 00:23:38,740
But the problem is
that the voice comes and goes.

335
00:23:39,050 --> 00:23:42,380
