338
00:23:49,360 --> 00:23:50,720
Yes.

339
00:23:51,530 --> 00:23:54,200
Mr Crick, I hate to sound
like a broken record...

340
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:56,490
...but that's schizophrenia.

341
00:23:57,900 --> 00:24:02,530
