350
00:24:34,040 --> 00:24:35,230
Okay.

351
00:24:36,140 --> 00:24:39,200
Yeah. That's a good idea.

352
00:24:39,910 --> 00:24:41,640
Thank you.

353
00:24:42,280 --> 00:24:45,080
So you're the gentleman
