- I don't know.

357
00:24:53,020 --> 00:24:56,290
Dramatic irony.
It'll fuck you every time.

358
00:24:57,290 --> 00:24:59,280
- So you crazy or what?
- Well...

359
00:24:59,490 --> 00:25:01,730
Are you allowed to say that
