369
00:25:20,820 --> 00:25:24,580
- How heartbreaking. Live alone?
- Yes.

370
00:25:25,890 --> 00:25:29,190
- Any pets?
- No.

371
00:25:29,560 --> 00:25:33,430
- Friends?
