379
00:25:51,610 --> 00:25:53,580
I wasn't counting the tiles.

380
00:25:55,020 --> 00:25:56,780
- Coffee?
- No, thank you.

381
00:25:56,980 --> 00:25:58,450
- Sure?
- Yes.

382
00:25:59,620 --> 00:26:02,290
So this woman, the voice,
told you you're gonna die?

383
00:26:02,290 --> 00:26:04,730
She didn't tell me.
She doesn't know I can hear her.

384
00:26:04,730 --> 00:26:06,520
- But she said it.
- Yes.

385
00:26:06,730 --> 00:26:08,110
And you believed her.

386
00:26:08,800 --> 00:26:10,800
