about a few other things.

387
00:26:10,800 --> 00:26:14,360
- Such as?
- How I felt about work.

388
00:26:14,570 --> 00:26:17,040
- You dislike your work?
- Yes.

389
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:21,510
Well, not the most insightful voice
in the world, is it?

390
00:26:21,510 --> 00:26:23,980
First thing on a list
of what Americans hate: Work.

391
00:26:23,980 --> 00:26:26,850
Second, traffic. Third, missing socks.
See what I'm saying?

392
00:26:26,850 --> 00:26:27,810
Sort of.

393
00:26:28,020 --> 00:26:30,220
