619
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:41,740
- It was fantastic.
- Just wondering if this nine is a seven.

620
00:40:41,740 --> 00:40:44,970
- And what did you do?
- I got a beautiful tan.

621
00:40:45,610 --> 00:40:49,830
- I'm just gonna guess it's a seven.
- I mean, I feel stress-free.

622
00:40:54,420 --> 00:40:56,200
Do you need help with that?

623
00:40:57,320 --> 00:40:59,560
- Walk to heaven. I see the president.

624
00:40:59,560 --> 00:41:01,930
- It's the taxman. Hello, Mr Taxman.
- Yeah.

625
00:41:01,930 --> 00:41:03,590
- You can call me Harold.
- Okay.

626
00:41:03,590 --> 00:41:05,430
- How the numbers going?
- Pretty good.

627
00:41:05,430 --> 00:41:07,400
- Gonna find that 22 percent?
- 22 percent?

628
00:41:07,400 --> 00:41:10,100
Twenty-two, 11 times 2.
It's prime numbers.

629
00:41:10,100 --> 00:41:13,300
- You gonna tax the bathroom?
- No, I'm not gonna tax the bathroom.

630
00:41:13,300 --> 00:41:15,770
- Could I use the bathroom, then?
- Go for it.

631
00:41:15,770 --> 00:41:17,670
Okay. I wanna use the bathroom.
Bye now.

632
00:41:17,670 --> 00:41:18,800
Bye-bye.

633
00:42:00,750 --> 00:42:02,120
Well, good night.

634
00:42:03,250 --> 00:42:04,910
You want a cookie?

635
00:42:05,560 --> 00:42:06,680
Oh, no.

636
00:42:06,890 --> 00:42:11,050
Come on. They're warm and gooey.
They're fresh out of the oven.

637
00:42:11,730 --> 00:42:13,530
No, I don't like cookies.

638
00:42:15,570 --> 00:42:17,190
You don't like cookies?

639
00:42:20,300 --> 00:42:23,400
- What's wrong with you?
- I don't know.

640
00:42:23,610 --> 00:42:26,540
- Everybody likes cookies.
- No, I know.

641
00:42:26,740 --> 00:42:30,650
I mean, after a really awful,
no-good day...

642
00:42:30,850 --> 00:42:34,080
...didn't your mama ever make you
milk and cookies?

643
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:38,410
No. My mother didn't bake.

644
00:42:38,620 --> 00:42:41,750
The only cookies I ever had
were store-bought.

645
00:42:44,290 --> 00:42:47,130
Okay. Sit down.

646
00:42:47,760 --> 00:42:49,890
- No, I'm...
