00:49:03,940 --> 00:49:06,450
- Don't do anything tomorrow.
- Nothing?

741
00:49:06,540 --> 00:49:11,000
Stay home. Don't answer the phone,
open the door, brush your teeth.

742
00:49:11,210 --> 00:49:12,820
- What about work?
- Call them.

743
00:49:12,820 --> 00:49:15,250
- Tell them you're not coming.
- Don't go to work?

744
00:49:15,250 --> 00:49:17,590
Don't do anything that may
