755
00:49:56,530 --> 00:50:00,400
<i>And it takes only seconds
for the fiddler crabs to realize...</i>

756
00:50:00,400 --> 00:50:02,930
<i>... that the wader
they might once have feared...</i>

757
00:50:02,930 --> 00:50:05,420
<i>... has now become their prey.</i>

758
00:50:06,770 --> 00:50:09,640
<i>The wounded bird knows its fate.</i>

759
00:50:10,610 --> 00:50:12,940
<i>Its desperate attempts to escape...</i>

760
00:50:12,940 --> 00:50:17,040
<i>... only underscore the hopelessness
of its plight.</i>

761
00:50:19,280 --> 00:50:24,090
<i>The primates' sad, soulful eyes
will be the first to be plucked out...</i>

762
00:50:24,090 --> 00:50:27,090
<i>... then sold to cosmetic companies
