766
00:50:38,940 --> 00:50:41,640
<i>Mr Zebra thought he was gonna
take a nice drink.</i>

767
00:50:41,640 --> 00:50:43,470
<i>But you never know
who's gonna eat...</i>

768
00:50:43,470 --> 00:50:45,940
<i>... when you're dining
at Mother Nature's restaurant.</i>

769
00:50:45,940 --> 00:50:48,850
<i>That's gotta hurt. What does
this bald eagle wanna serve...</i>

770
00:50:48,850 --> 00:50:51,080
<i>... with some kidney beans
