771
00:50:51,080 --> 00:50:55,070
<i>It's an eel. And again:</i>

772
00:50:55,290 --> 00:50:57,750
<i>Looks like old Mr Crocodile
wanted some antelope...</i>

773
00:50:57,750 --> 00:50:59,990
<i>... to clear that salty zebra
from his palate.</i>

774
00:50:59,990 --> 00:51:03,560
<i>Here's a struggle betting gentlemen
