775
00:51:03,560 --> 00:51:07,500
<i>When a mongoose encounters a cobra
it's hard to know who's gonna win.</i>

776
00:51:07,500 --> 00:51:09,870
<i>But this time it looks like
it's... the cobra...</i>

777
00:51:09,870 --> 00:51:12,170
<i>... who's putting the squeeze
